snippet.textDisplay: Problem is bombay jayashree should have been given equal space as richa. Otherwise it looks like richa stealing the show everytime. Jayashree is traditional classical singer ,they need to be used intelligently and carefully. Richa is versatile ,she could fit herself in any song. Though jayashree held her own ,richa's alap at end took the limelight ultimately. A classical duet between these two would've been better. That would've been an equal competition
